ümber sisemiste, nagu merikarp,

00:06:11.776 --> 00:06:13.136
ja seda nimetatakse,

00:06:13.216 --> 00:06:14.366
kuulake nüüd,

00:06:15.006 --> 00:06:16.400
The Barbie

00:06:16.560 --> 00:06:17.536
(Oiged)

00:06:17.836 --> 00:06:20.106
